== 社會評論 ==
Twitch Film的Rodney Perkins評論：「這部電影沒有什麼突破性」，並認為儘管L的角色忠於原著，但他的特質卻不明顯。<ref name="twitchreview">{{cite web |url=http://twitchfilm.com/reviews/2008/08/affd-review-l-change-the-world.php |title=AFFD Review: L: CHANGE THE WORLD |accessdate=2011-11-25 |work=Twitch Film |date=2008-08-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120628050128/http://twitchfilm.com/reviews/2008/08/affd-review-l-change-the-world.php |archivedate=2012-06-28 }}</ref> Love HK Films的評論家Kozo也認為這部電影是「給粉絲的殺必死」，沒有什麼突破性也不值得關注。<ref name="lovehkfilm">{{cite web |url=http://www.lovehkfilm.com/panasia/l_change_the_world.html |title=L: Change the World review |accessdate=2011-11-25 |work=Love HK Film |year=2008 |archive-date=2021-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210102195650/http://lovehkfilm.com/panasia/l_change_the_world.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。本片在2008年第五屆[[報知蛇莓獎|報知蛇莓獎]]獲頒該年度最差電影作品、最差導演、最差男主角<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.sina.com/oth/phoenixtv/506-104-103-108/2008-12-21/23103511015.html |title=日金酸莓評選出爐 《死亡筆記》外傳遭批不倫不類 |access-date=2014-09-07 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304102612/http://news.sina.com/oth/phoenixtv/506-104-103-108/2008-12-21/23103511015.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

